  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Welcome to Hometopia</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The ultimate free-form building game where your creativity knows no bounds. Forget life simulation distractions; here, it’s all about pure, uninterrupted creative freedom to design and build the home of your dreams. Unleash your inner architect, express your unique style, and collaborate with friends in real-time multiplayer. From cozy cottages to sprawling modern mansions, your vision becomes reality in a community of passionate Topians. Build without limits and share your creations with the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1138640/extras/12de5301c4564747bbcd8c79585da0b4.poster.avif?t=1743629398\" width=600 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1138640/extras/12de5301c4564747bbcd8c79585da0b4.webm?t=1743629398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Experience True Creative Freedom in Sandbox Mode</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Design your dream home with no constraints, an unlimited budget, and endless possibilities. Build in any style that matches your taste, from classic to contemporary, with stunning high-fidelity graphics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1138640/extras/93f91248c5c287b2fa9f5b28b00275ef.poster.avif?t=1743629398\" width=600 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1138640/extras/93f91248c5c287b2fa9f5b28b00275ef.webm?t=1743629398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Collaborate or Create Solo</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Team up with friends to tackle massive projects, design entire neighborhoods, or simply decorate a home together. Prefer to work alone? The choice is yours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1138640/extras/8094a33308eb247fbbe87569df6917a6.poster.avif?t=1743629398\" width=600 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1138640/extras/8094a33308eb247fbbe87569df6917a6.webm?t=1743629398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Show Off Your Interior Design Skills</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize everything with thousands of objects at your fingertips. Experiment with countless styles, layouts, and themes to create the perfect fit for every space.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1138640/extras/f4efd7eefbd3b5929bdedb2e10f06926.poster.avif?t=1743629398\" width=600 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1138640/extras/f4efd7eefbd3b5929bdedb2e10f06926.webm?t=1743629398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Jumpstart Your Vision with Ready-Made Homes</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use pre-built houses as inspiration or a foundation for your next masterpiece. Decorate, customize, and transform them to match your unique vision.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1138640/extras/264527dfeb1a27e9ff4f59b6a6871f11.poster.avif?t=1743629398\" width=600 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1138640/extras/264527dfeb1a27e9ff4f59b6a6871f11.webm?t=1743629398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Personalize Every Detail</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from any color, pattern, or texture to make your designs truly one of a kind. Every detail is yours to shape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1138640/extras/c751ac5fbed6d18842e3a231796448ee.poster.avif?t=1743629398\" width=600 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1138640/extras/c751ac5fbed6d18842e3a231796448ee.webm?t=1743629398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Capture and Share Your Creations</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the built-in camera tool to snap stunning photos of your spaces. Share your work with the world and inspire others in the Hometopia community.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1138640/extras/d138b89f747a2a75e45ad73e6bcef4da.poster.avif?t=1743629398\" width=600 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1138640/extras/d138b89f747a2a75e45ad73e6bcef4da.webm?t=1743629398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Build Inside and Out</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don’t stop at the walls! Create breathtaking outdoor spaces with Hometopia’s powerful landscaping tools. Design lush gardens, stylish patios, and dreamy backyards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1138640/extras/93bac582ca3aea1660ddea70591a95d0.poster.avif?t=1743629398\" width=600 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1138640/extras/93bac582ca3aea1660ddea70591a95d0.webm?t=1743629398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Create and Showcase Your Portfolio</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compile your favorite builds into a stunning portfolio that you can share with the world. Let your designs shine and inspire others!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1138640/extras/03e58d32f0abc1d9c7b4b79e0345a155.poster.avif?t=1743629398\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1138640/extras/03e58d32f0abc1d9c7b4b79e0345a155.webm?t=1743629398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1138640/extras/03e58d32f0abc1d9c7b4b79e0345a155.mp4?t=1743629398\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you’re building solo or with friends, <strong>Hometopia</strong> offers endless possibilities to craft, create, and share your dream homes. Start your journey today and join a thriving community of creators!</p>",
